client

Class MovaClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.MovaClient

  • public class MovaClient
extends java.lang.Object
    This class uses the jersey client to access the application server's web services. It converts MOVA objects into JSON Objects and uses REST API to POST, GET, PUT and DELETE Resources

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      MovaClient()
      Creates a new MOVA client containing a MOVA to JSON Serializer and a Jersey Client to access server web services
